Based on the information provided in VAT returns and testimonials, qualified auditors select the cases to be audited and ensure the applicable taxation.
In order to reduce revenue shortfalls in VAT and at the same time increase the risk of being discovered for unreliable entrepreneurs, appropriate management processes and risk management systems should be introduced.
